      "chapterTitle": "1.1 什么是GitHub",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "26211801_9_2297-2358",
          "range": "2297-2358",
          "rangeStart": 2297,
          "rangeEnd": 2358,
          "markText": "在Git中，开发者将源代码存入名叫“Git仓库”的资料库中并加以使用。而GitHub则是在网络上提供Git仓库的一项服务。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1770085280,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2026-02-03 10:21:20",
